\cs15\fs16\insrsid16264423 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16264423 Vanishing Indian}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10764711 
\par 
\par PERCY W. HALL.
